OL,3,CBergerac is back as release date
OL,4,Cconfirmed for new drama series
OL,6,FFans of the Jersey crime drama
OL,7,FBergerac will not have to wait much
OL,8,Flonger for a new series as the show's
OL,9,Frelease date has been confirmed.
OL,11,FAfter more than 30 years, the
OL,12,Fdetective will return to UK screens on
OL,13,FThursday 27 February through the free
OL,14,Fstreaming platform U.
OL,16,FDeals have also been struck with
OL,17,Fseveral international broadcasters
OL,18,Fincluding ABC in Australia, TVNZ in
OL,19,FNew Zealand and BBC First in Poland.
