OL,6,FDamien Molony will star as Jim
OL,7,FBergerac in the reimagined show with
OL,8,FZoe Wanamaker and Philip Glenister
OL,9,Falso part of the cast.
OL,11,FThe remake will focus on one case
OL,12,Fthroughout the series as Bergerac
OL,13,Fbattles his own struggles while
OL,14,Finvestigating the murder of a woman
OL,15,Ffrom a rich Jersey family.
